location.fullValue: The 1657 with 2 car garage Plan, Faraday Hills Homes in Estacada OR

data.description: Gorgeous one level home located on premium 0.16 size corner lot! This home has been meticulously maintained and upgraded from head to toe including top of line Solar Panels!! Stunning one level with 9 foot ceilings, luxury vinyl plank flooring, quartz countertops, upgraded tile backsplash, upgraded carpet pad in bedrooms, custom finishes in each bathroom. Inviting family room with custom fireplace/mantle & luxury vinyl plank flooring leads to your light and bright kitchen complete with island, farm sink, upgraded tile backsplash, pantry and all kitchen appliances included! Primary suite includes recessed ceilings, ceiling fan capable, walk in closet, beautiful tile countertops and tile flooring. Upgraded carpet pad in all bedrooms! Fully fenced 2800 sq ft sod backyard with french drain and 12x12 concrete patio perfect for summer nights! Premium large lot complete with sprinkler system to keep your lawn looking spectacular! Garage with additional storage. Solar panels make energy bill only $10/month!! Come tour this beauty!
